Puggi: ...But why do I still feel like it's missing something?
???: Dora! Dora!
: For your convenience, we've translated the rest of the Dora-speak into English.
Puggi: You say I'm not the Main Character!? Where do you get the nerve!? Is this your rebellious phase or something!?
Big-Horn-Dora: Stuff it, you're not my dad! Where's the real Mandora King!?
Doofy-Dora: Get outta here!
Big-Horn-Dora: I'm a real, chosen Mandora! You're not our leader! I challenge you to a duel, loser leaves this land!
Puggi: Ah, yes, the fate of the Main Character~
Puggi: A new challenger approaches, and I must swat him into the stars...
Puggi: You've got spunk, kid, but it'll take more than that to dethrone me!
Big-Horn-Dora: What is our hero doing over there by that faker...? He must be defeated...
Guard-Dora: Does anyone have anything to say before the competition begins?
Puggi: You steppin' into the kitchen, get ready to be fried up, yo!
Big-Horn-Dora: Enough nonsense, let's do this!
Guard-Dora: Well then, let the duel begin!
Guard-Dora: The winner is... Puggi!
Big-Horn-Dora: Why... I trained for so long...
Puggi: Training alone isn't going to get you anywhere! You've gotta listen to me if you wanna get strong!
Big-Horn-Dora: ...Really? Am I really too weak to be a leader?
Puggi: (Man, these kids and their rebellious phases, so annoying...)
Puggi: Listen, kid, you might be a supporting character now, but maybe once I go you can step up to the plate.
Big-Horn-Dora: ...After you go?
Puggi: As the main character, this is only a short stop on my journey.
Big-Horn-Dora: Then... then teach me, please! I want to get stronger!
Puggi: Very well, since you are so eager. I'll teach you a thing or two... when I have the time.
Big-Horn-Dora: Yay!
Puggi: Shoulda just listened to me from the start, instead of making a big fuss about everything...
Puggi: Hmph, alright. Get ready for Puggi Boot Camp!!
